import React from 'react' const Rating = ({value, text}) => { return (
= 1 ? "fas fa-star" : value >= 0.5 ? "fa-star-half-alt" : "fas fa-star"} > = 2 ? "fas fa-star" : value >= 1.5 ? "fas fa-star-half-alt" : "fas fa-star"} > = 3 ? "fas fa-star" : value >= 2.5 ? "fas fa-star-half-alt" : "fas fa-star"} > = 4 ? "fas fa-star" : value >= 3.5 ? "fas fa-star-half-alt" : "fas fa-star"} > = 5 ? "fas fa-star" : value >= 4.5 ? "fa-star-half-alt" : "fas fa-star"} > {text && text}
) } export default Rating
